Cell["\<\
To improve the accuracy of the scan over the orbit-space surface (function \
wbBrancNecCond3), the scanning grid can be refined by adjusting the parameter \
values of stepsWein. Note that increasing these values also increases the \
computation time. For most practical applications, the default settings \
(stepsBranc = {17, 15}) are sufficient; however, to achieve accuracy close \
100% it may be necessary to increase them, for example to stepsWein = {50, \
80}.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978670763710136*^9, 3.978670847816402*^9}, 
   3.9786711743764887`*^9, {3.978671205798896*^9, 3.978671351818645*^9}, {
   3.978671387614222*^9, 3.978671406147262*^9}, {3.978671466689073*^9, 
