Cell["\<\
Couplings are generated to satisfy the UNI and NCL1 conditions, and are then \
filtered to retain only those that also satisfy the NCL2-NCL3 or sufficient \
BFB conditions:\
\>", "Text",
 Editable->True,
 TaggingRules->{},
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.954599430847682*^9, 3.9545994368102837`*^9}, {
